The district of '''Brig''' is a district in the [[canton of Valais]], [[Switzerland]].  It has a population of {{Swiss populations|CH-VS|B2301}} (as of {{Swiss populations date|CH-VS}}).{{Swiss populations ref|CH-VS}}

==Municipalities==
It includes the following [[Communes of Switzerland|municipalities]]:

